{"lemma":"عِتْقُ","slug":"عِتْقُ","root":"ع.ت.ق","root_slug":"ع-ت-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ت-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n27960","n27961","n27962"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%AA%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27960","headword_ar":"عُتْقٌ","root":"Etq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n27961","headword_ar":"عِتْقٌ","root":"Etq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned above as an inf. n. and also as a simple subst. (see 1)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najaAbapN","text_ar":"نَجَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as a quality of a horse and the like, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Generousness, excellence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swiftness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 1, first and second sentences]. (K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karamN","text_ar":"كَرَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Generousness, generosity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nobility"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, Mgh, O, K;) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^aboyana AlEitoqa fiY wajohi fulaAnK","text_ar":"مَا اَبْيَنَ العِتْقَ فِى وَجْهِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How manifest is generousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the face of such a one!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arafN","text_ar":"شَرَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Highness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eminence, of rank"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beauty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comeliness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) ―         -b5-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, of freedom; contr. of slavery."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) ―         -b6-  [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Oldness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in which sense,] accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EitoqN","text_ar":"عِتْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EutoqN","text_ar":"عُتْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"relate to inanimate things, as wine and dates; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qidamN","text_ar":"قِدَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"relates to inanimate things and also to animals. (L, K.)       -A2-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EutuqN","text_ar":"عُتُقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of trees from which Arabian bows are made:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, K: *) the name being meant to imply the excellence of the bow [made therefrom]. (AHn.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n27962","headword_ar":"عُتُقٌ","root":"Etq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next precedes."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}